This is the workflow that actually works in the real world.

Step 1 — The user accesses the repo THEMSELVES

On iPad or desktop:

- Open GitHub
• Navigate to the Legal‑Calculus repo
• Open the file they want
• Copy/paste the text or download/upload the file into Copilot

This is the only way content enters Copilot.

Copilot cannot fetch it.
Copilot cannot browse it.
Copilot cannot open it.

The user brings the artifact.

