Step 2 — Copilot Pro becomes the “thinking engine”

Once the user pastes a file, Copilot Pro can:

- analyze
• rewrite
• structure
• map doctrine
• build modules
• stress‑test arguments
• generate curriculum
• create Blueprint AI workflows
• integrate with the LCES Shield Protocol

This is where Copilot Pro is better than any other AI:

It handles long reasoning, legal structure, multi‑layer logic, and procedural literacy.

Other AIs collapse into chat mode.
Copilot Pro stays in system‑building mode.

