Step 3 — The user decides what goes back into the repo

Copilot never pushes to GitHub.

The user:

- copies the improved file
• pastes it back into GitHub
• commits the change
• maintains the archive

This preserves:

- version control
• authorship
• transparency
• procedural integrity

This is exactly what Legal‑Calculus teaches:
Human intelligence controls the record.

